Package solver.reachablepoints.graph.board

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IEdge
    Empty interface to generalize abstract and concrete edges
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractEdge
    An AbstractEdge that is the edge of a Node.
    AffectedEdgesLookUpTable
    provides a Look-Up-Table to determine all edges that use a specific node.
    ConcreteEdge
    A ConcreteEdge linkes two nodes in the board graph via the properties speed, direciotn and doJump.
    Graph
    A board that interprets the game as a graph.
    Node
    A cell of a board that holds information about all possible paths starting here.
